name: Plan.Set.Go
tag_list: plansetgo, psg, planning, replan, ideas, share, friends, strangers, anyone, discover, adventure, travel, weddings
overview:
Plan.Set.Go. lets you plan anything with anyone from around the world - including your friends or people you’ve never met. People use PSG to plan trips, weddings, dinners, hair style changes… the list goes on.

The really fun and exciting part is that you can receive help from friends and/or people around the world when planning. Pay it forward by joining someone else’s plans and giving your ideas and suggestions, or “replan” anything you find interesting or relevant to your own plans.
